<p>[3].“幽门螺杆菌胃炎京都全球共识”解读.胃肠病学.2015. </p>
<p>[4].第五次全国幽门螺杆菌感染处理共识报告.中华消化杂志.2017. </p>
<p>[5].ACG(美国胃肠病学学院) 临床指南: 幽门螺杆菌感染的治疗.胃肠病学和肝病学杂志.2017. </p>
<p>[6].Joint ESPGHAN/NASPGHAN Guidelines for the Management of Helicobacter pylori in Children and Adolescents (Update 2016).JPGN 2017. </p>
<p>[7].Jones N L, Koletzko S, Goodman K, et al. Joint ESPGHAN/NASPGHAN guidelines for the management of Helicobacter pylori in children and adolescents (update 2016)[J]. Journal of pediatric gastroenterology and nutrition, 2017, 64(6): 991-1003. </p>
